Tapanui flu
Homonym Number:
Word Class: noun
Sense Number:
Definition:a common name for a group of symptoms otherwise called the myalgic encephalomyelitis (ME) syndrome. [from Tapanui, a town in Southland]
Origin: [none]
Register:
